    "Subsequently, the accuracy and comprehensiveness of the generated functional analysis were evaluated according to the metrics outlined in Section title \"Functional analysis generation evaluation\" by a TRIZ evaluator.",
    "Table 9 illustrates the accuracy and comprehensiveness of the functional analysis produced with and without the interaction extraction module.",
    "As demonstrated in the table, both the accuracy and comprehensiveness of the functional analysis diminished in the absence of the module.",
